---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About — Luigi Bifulco"
  description="Luigi Bifulco, software craftsman and technical architect. Complicating is easy, simplifying is hard."
  lang="en"
  altUrl="/about/"
>
  <section class="about">
    <img class="portrait" src="/images/luigi.jpg" alt="Luigi Bifulco" width="480" height="480" />
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>Hi, I'm Luigi.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Software craftsman, DDD practitioner, agile enthusiast.
      Full-stack: Java, .NET, Angular, React. Naples, Italy.
    </p>

    <blockquote class="motto">
      &ldquo;Complicating is easy,<br />simplifying is hard.&rdquo;
    </blockquote>

    <p>
      That's my motto, and the common thread of almost twenty years of building
      software: a methodical, careful approach, attention to detail, clean and
      maintainable code. Today I'm a Software Engineer and Technical Architect
      at <a href="https://it.linkedin.com/company/infominds-spa">INFOMINDS
      SpA</a>, working on a cloud solution built on Domain-Driven Design
      principles — with responsibilities spanning architecture to frontend, and
      with AI methodically integrated into my workflow as an architectural
      partner, not just a writing assistant.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before that: digital signatures and certificates at InfoCert, business
      intelligence at CCH Tagetik and Wolters Kluwer, large-scale frontend for
      banking and telco at NTT DATA — and even earlier, the Java world, GWT and
      the first build tools you can read about in this blog's oldest posts. I
      graduated in Computer Science at the University of Salerno.
    </p>
    <p>
      This blog was born years ago on Kirby CMS and has been reborn as a static
      site: markdown, git, and nothing to maintain. Just the way I like it.
    </p>

    <ul class="links">
      <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/luigibifulco/">LinkedIn</a></li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/gigibiffi84">GitHub</a></li>
      <li><a href="mailto:bifulcoluigi@gmail.com">Email</a></li>
      <li><a href="/rss.xml">RSS</a></li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about { padding: 5rem 0 2rem; }
  .portrait {
    width: 7.5rem;
    height: 7.5rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
  }
  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 9vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    line-height: 1.05;
  }
  .lead {
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
    max-width: 34rem;
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    line-height: 1.45;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .motto {
    margin: 3.5rem 0;
    padding: 0;
    border: none;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.1rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: 1.25;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .about p:not(.lead):not(.eyebrow) {
    max-width: 38rem;
    font-size: 1.06rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 3rem 0 0;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.8rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .links a {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--fg);
    border: 1px solid var(--hairline);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.45rem 1.1rem;
    transition: all 0.25s ease;
  }
  .links a:hover {
    background: var(--fg);
    color: var(--bg);
    border-color: var(--fg);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .about { padding: 3rem 0 1.5rem; }
    .portrait { width: 6rem; height: 6rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .lead { font-size: 1.15rem; }
    .motto { font-size: 1.35rem; margin: 2.5rem 0; }
  }
</style>
